name: Michelle Limacan
description: i would describe myself as a happy person, intelligent, well educated, stylish, sociable, attractive, caring and clean. I..m open-minded, sensitive, truthful, passionate, with a great sense of humor …responsible and serious when I have to be. I love music, arts, fashion, traveling, meeting people and all is beautiful ! I am looking for that special someone, I could love with all my heart, body and soul. I love to find experiences and to share them with someone close, but I have no special person in my life to share my dreams and excitements witha good relationship provide stimulation at the intellectual, emotional and physical level
